<view class="container">
  <view class="page-header">
    <view class="page-title">Markdown 转 PDF / Word</view>
    <view class="page-desc">支持表格、代码块、任务列表、删除线，可直接导入 .md 文件继续导出。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="card form-card header-card">
    <text class="label">文档标题</text>
    <input class="title-input" placeholder="给文档起个名字" value="{{ title }}" bindinput="onTitleInput" maxlength="50" />
  </view>

  <view class="card form-card">
    <view class="card-head">
      <view class="card-title">Markdown 内容</view>
      <view class="counter">{{ content.length }}/200000</view>
    </view>

    <textarea
      class="md-input"
      value="{{ content }}"
      bindinput="onContentInput"
      placeholder="在这里写 Markdown..."
      auto-height
      maxlength="-1"
    />

    <view class="tool-row">
      <button class="mini-action" bindtap="chooseMdFile">导入 MD 文件</button>
      <button class="mini-action" bindtap="loadSample">载入示例</button>
      <button class="mini-action danger" bindtap="clearAll">清空</button>
    </view>

    <view class="notice notice-info notice-box">
      <view class="notice-head">
        <view class="notice-icon">i</view>
        <view class="notice-title">导出说明</view>
      </view>
      <view class="notice-text">适合笔记、说明文档、表格内容快速导出；PDF 更适合分享，Word 更适合后续编辑。</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="footer-actions">
    <button class="btn btn-primary {{ submitting ? 'btn-disabled' : '' }}" bindtap="exportPdf" loading="{{ submitting }}" disabled="{{ submitting }}">导出 PDF</button>
    <button class="btn btn-secondary" bindtap="exportWord" loading="{{ submitting }}" disabled="{{ submitting }}">导出 Word</button>
  </view>
</view>
